author: jdcasey
msg: Cleaning up the use of MavenResourcesExecution and MavenFileFilterRequest, and moving the new getDefaultFilterWrappers(..) call to use a common base class of these two execution requests: AbstractMavenFilteringRequest. Also, adding options to enable the request to turn on/off injection of POM build/filters (in cases where these are already in the filters list, it doesn't make sense to re-add them).
